version_description:
We update the app to add some new features :
1. More rights and interests for the sellers;
2. More powerful member operations to increase the ROI;
3. Mobile performance optimization to run quicker.

We update the app to add some new features :
1. More Flow displacement rights for the sellers;
2. Fixed some known issues.

We update the app to add some new features :
1. Entries for important system message types;
2. More Flow displacement rights for the sellers;
3. Fixed some known issues.

After the big redecoration, the app focuses more on the "sellers-centered" concept:
1. Outstanding items, official announcements and irregularities information are highlighted, and important matters are not omitted;
2. Adapt to the new exciting visual style.

The brand-new Qianniu 9.0 version, supporting complete the entire chain operation of the store management with mobile phones, is more concise and efficient!
1. Homepage:
        1) Pull down to view the entire store's operating data, and grasp the store dynamics;
        2) New module "Operation Recommendations" to help businesses master online shop operating skills;
        3) Added official tools covering whole store operations: store opening, merchandise management, transaction, refund, evaluation, account management, event registration, etc.;
2. Message module:
        1) Input automatic association shortcut phrases to improve reception efficiency;
        2) Long press to add a star to mark important customers;
        3) Re-integration of system messages;
3. Marketing module:
        1) Integrated multi-channel marketing function, a marketing page with site traffic, efficient promotion, and customer acquisition on;
        2) Quick sharing to help merchants quickly obtain off-site users;
        3) Joint service providers to provide a variety of marketing tools;
        4) Collect commodity operations methodology and provide diversified commodity promoting solutions;
4. Toutiao module:
        1) Toutiao has been upgraded, providing new sections such as the latest, Q&A, quality courses, lives, etc.;
        2) Provide the latest news of Taobao, while courses/lives to enhance your business capabilities;
5. Merchandise release and management tools:
        1) Support multiple publishing methods such as scanning codes and taking photos, and intelligent matting to improve efficiency;
        2) Real-time editing and saving to prevent mistakenly closing pictures;
        3) New Picture Space to connect pictures between PC and mobile;
        4) Quick send the same merchandise, quickly set specifications, inventory and price batch set; batch inventory management, improving the efficiency of mobile merchandise management;
6. Transaction management:
        1) Remark, change the price of, and close unpaid orders;
        2) Support deliver goods through scanning logistic codes, mailing address change, multi-parcel split delivery, and logistics number change;
        3) The new refund tool;
7. Reviews management:
        1) View credit scores, store levels, DSR dynamic scores, and reviews data statistics;
        2) Reply and batch operate the reviews;
        3) Introduce "response templates" to quickly complete the response;
8. Account management:
        1) Support mobile phone number and scan face login;
        2) Create, manage, and set permissions of sub-accounts;
        3) Complete approval tasks initiated by various accounts;
Many official tools, such as shipping templates, address management, picture space, coupons, shop decoration, and so on, will be launched soon. Welcome to experience the brand-new Qianniu 9.0 version.
